description: Northern Ocean Ltd. provides offshore contract drilling services for the oil and gas industry worldwide. The company owns and operates two semi-submersible rigs. It also invests in power generation solutions. The company was incorporated in 2017 and is based in Hamilton, Bermuda. Northern Ocean Ltd. is a subsidiary of Hemen Holding Limited.
